file_content.text: Six more votes, and the Outer Rim would have had a dedicated patrol. Just six.
Nothing gets a majority these days. Everyone's looking out for their own interests.
It's not even election season. We can't accomplish anything without a unified body.
Do they think they'll get to keep their seats if the Empire comes back?
The possibility doesn't seem to scare certain Senators whose names and planets I won't mention....
